.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, iced-tea, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, skydiving, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, surfing, skiing, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking juice##2
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | cola      | juice       | iced-tea   |
| Hobby      | cooking   | hiking  | filmmaking | skydiving     |
| Sport      | surfing     | climbing | skiing        | biathlon |

