.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, peach, potato, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, singing, hiking, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person eating apple is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person eating peach##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's sport is rugby##2
6. the person eating peach is between the person eating apple and the person eating potato##2
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | potato | peach  | apple | strawberry      |
| Hobby   | hiking  | rock-climbing  | sudoku | singing |
| Sport   | surfing | biathlon | parkour | rugby     |

