.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, apple, grapes, asparagus
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, fantasy, comedy, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, lacrosse, tennis, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person eating apple is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
7. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | grapes  | apple    | asparagus | lemon  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | sports       | fantasy        | crime    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | rugby | rowing  | tennis |

