.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, puzzles, baking, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero, sports, satire
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, dog, goat
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is between the owner of the goat and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks  | puzzles | baking | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | satire | superhero   | sports         |
| Pet           | bird | dog  | frog   | goat      |

