2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person eating blueberry##1
3. the fan of metal is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating radish##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | radish  | blueberry    | corn | kiwi       |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | reading  | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | disco      | metal  | d&b     |

