3. the person eating plum is between the person eating potato and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is chess##1
8. the person watching superhero movies is the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
