.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, broccoli, cranberry, grapefruit
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, woodworking, collecting, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, pony, bird
1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
2. the owner of the pony is the person eating broccoli##1
3. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the owner of the turtle and the person eating grapefruit##2
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the bird##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the snake##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | grapefruit  | cranberry | zucchini | broccoli     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | collecting   | magic-tricks  | woodworking    |
| Pet     | snake        | bird       | turtle      | pony |

