3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking coffee and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | coffee     | iced-tea | fanta       |
| Hobby      | writing  | board-games | camping  | woodworking |
| Pet        | hedgehog  | ferret      | snake        | goldfish      |

