3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the horse##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite | coffee  | hot-chocolate       | 7up   |
| Hobby      | singing     | skydiving | puzzles | board-games |
| Pet        | horse        | guinea-pig | dog     | fish |

