.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, architect, freelancer, firefighter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, family, scientific, thriller
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, van, quad-bike
1. the person watching action movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the van is the freelancer##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the electrician##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the scooter is between the person watching scientific movies and the freelancer##2
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the scooter is the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | architect | firefighter | freelancer    | electrician   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific      | family   | thriller | action |
| Transport     | roller     | scooter       | van        | quad-bike    |

