1. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is the software-developer##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the coach and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
6. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | photography   | hiking           | board-games         | writing      |
| Job     | coach | dancer | software-developer | videographer |
| Sport   | skateboarding     | basketball         | baseball       | handball        |

