.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, milk, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, dubstep, ambient, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian, pakistani, thai
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking water is between the person drinking milk and the malaysian##2
3. the person drinking milk is the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person drinking milk is between the fan of ambient and the thai##2
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
6. the japanese is between the pakistani and the fan of r&b##2
7. the fan of hip-hop is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk | water   | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | dubstep    | ambient   | r&b     |
| Nationality   | thai  | pakistani | japanese | malaysian   |

