.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, water
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, avocado, eggplant, cherry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, golf, snowboarding
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
2. the person eating eggplant is between the person drinking water and the person who's sport is golf##2
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | hot-chocolate | water           | iced-tea |
| Food       | pomegranate | eggplant    | avocado          | cherry   |
| Sport      | golf  | rowing   | snowboarding | biathlon  |

