4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person watching family movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the owner of the rat is between the person drinking water and the owner of the goldfish##2
7. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
