4. the person driving the ship is the coach##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | software-developer        | coach  | designer | electrician   |
| Sport       | climbing | biathlon | rowing    | rugby |
| Transport   | van        | ship     | motorbike       | boat      |

