.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, plum, peach, eggplant
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, turtle, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, airplane, quad-bike, van
1. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
2. the person eating mango is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the van is the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the ferret is between the person eating eggplant and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | eggplant | plum | mango | peach |
| Pet         | dog       | ferret     | turtle   | chinchilla   |
| Transport   | boat | airplane | quad-bike | van |

 